# KeepnetLabs Vue 2 Frontend Development Rules

## рџЋЇ PROJECT OVERVIEW

The project aims to develop a **KeepnetLabs Human Risk Management** platform for web users.
**Mission:** Transform human risk into human resilience.

Phishing, socialвЂ‘engineering and user error still trigger the majority of breaches.
The platform reframes this as a humanвЂ‘risk problem and couples continuous measurement with adaptive controls to shrink that risk over time.
AIвЂ‘driven "bestвЂ‘ofвЂ‘suite" platform that unifies training, behavioural telemetry and automated controls under one console.

### Core Benefits
- **Quantify human risk:** Individual & orgвЂ‘level risk scores pull from phishing tests, password hygiene, email behaviour and policy violations
- **Lower breach probability:** Average PhishвЂ‘prone % drops from >30% to <5% in 12 months when programmes run continuously
- **Reduce incidentвЂ‘response effort:** Automates triage & remediation of >85% of userвЂ‘reported emails

### Scale & Performance Requirements
- **1,000 organizations** and **500,000 users**
- **95% user engagement**, **99.9% uptime**, **10,000 monthly risk assessments**
- **<1000ms response time** for real-time analytics

